&lt;li&gt;Define and own the global partnerships strategy, covering partner segmentation, prioritisation, tiering, commercial model, lifecycle, operating cadence, and go-to-market approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take direct accountability for meeting partnership-sourced and partnership-influenced pipeline and revenue targets&lt;/li&gt;
